'''Azeqziq''' deg [[tasnignewt|tesnignewt]] d tudra (aṣubbu) n [[aman|waman]] [[aneznez|yettwaneznezn]] s talɣa n [[ageffur|ugeffur]] neɣ n [[adfel|wedfel]], Tasmekta n uzeqziq d tin yemgaraden gar tama ar tayeṭṭ s unect (ɛla ḥsab) n [[anezwu|unezwu]] n yal tama.

Yettili-d wakat n uzeqziq ɣef tjumma tusbiṭ s [[tigget]] n [[millimiter|mn]].

